    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Builder
    An abstract base class for constructing and finalizing an object or process.
    Column
    Column represents a column in a table structure.
    CSVExporter
    The CSVExporter class provides functionality to export Table data to a CSV (Comma-Separated Values) file.
    DSLException
    Custom exception class for handling DSL-related errors.
    DSLParser
    This class is responsible for parsing a custom Domain-Specific Language (DSL) PREQL and translating the parsed structure into a series of builder operations to process data tables.
    Exporter
    The Exporter class provides base functionality for exporting Table data.
    ExportException
    Custom exception class for handling export-related errors.
    FileParser
    Abstract class FileParser provides functionality for parsing data from a file into a Table object.
    HTMLExporter
    The HTMLExporter class provides functionality for exporting Table data into an HTML format, where each table's columns are displayed in an HTML table.
    ImportBuilder
    A builder class for importing table data from files and directories.
    ImportException
    Custom exception class for handling import-related errors.
    JSONExporter
    The JSONExporter class provides functionality for exporting a Table to a JSON format.
    JSONParser
    JSONParser is a subclass of FileParser that provides functionality for parsing data from JSON files.
    Main
     
    OperationBuilder
    A builder class for performing operations on tables and columns.
    OperationException
    Custom exception class for handling operation-related errors.
    Parser
    Parser is a utility class responsible for parsing files based on their extension.
    ParserException
    Custom exception class for handling errors during parsing operations.
    SelectBuilder
    The SelectBuilder class allows for building and applying select operations on a set of tables.
    SelectException
    Custom exception class for handling select-related errors.
    Table
    Table represents a table structure with columns and rows.
    TableBuilder
    The TableBuilder class provides a builder pattern for constructing, configuring, and exporting tables in various formats.
    Utils
    Utils is a utility class providing common file and path-related methods.
    XMLExporter
    The XMLExporter class provides functionality for exporting a Table to an XML format.
    XMLParser
    XMLParser is a subclass of FileParser responsible for parsing XML files.
    YAMLParser
    YAMLParser is a subclass of FileParser responsible for parsing YAML files.
